  "text": [
    "1 Kinship:",
    "Is embarrassing the wind,",
    "Like dead black boys,",
    "Falling down from the trees,",
    "Then downstream\u2013",
    "On their knees,",
    "Blood like,",
    "Like a rich nation.",
    "2 Metaphor:",
    "Becomes humiliating,",
    "And clean,",
    "Ticking like a ripe machine.",
    "Do not",
    "Bend,",
    "Fold,",
    "Or mutilate me\u2013",
    "This is your future speaking.",
    "3 The air smells so metaphysical",
    "We have accused it\u2013",
    "Of smog,",
    "And lost manhood,",
    "Then all ritual.",
    "4 Whoever wrote:",
    "A view is a mountain speaking",
    "But left the introduction",
    "For the snow,",
    "And accused silence",
    "Of its soul.",
    "5 The whole nation:",
    "Is a stanza of blackness,",
    "A huge white whale,",
    "Faith in space",
    "(Like the newspapers),",
    "And the quiet insistence",
    "We have peace,",
    "And it\u2019s your world, brother."
  ],
